1
00:00:03,770 --> 00:00:06,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's give them everything we've got.</font>

2
00:00:06,260 --> 00:00:07,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here we go.</font>

3
00:00:07,730 --> 00:00:09,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Evilly!</font>

4
00:00:10,070 --> 00:00:12,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bloody!</font>

5
00:00:12,860 --> 00:00:15,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fantastic!</font>

6
00:00:16,630 --> 00:00:22,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Neuntöte!</font>

7
00:00:31,670 --> 00:00:36,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder if those boys are really 
doing their best to protect Lynn.</font>

8
00:00:39,890 --> 00:00:43,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Lynn. Protect.</font>

9
00:00:43,770 --> 00:00:45,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you very much, guys!</font>

10
00:00:46,800 --> 00:00:48,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Little Red!</font>

11
00:00:48,170 --> 00:00:51,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please wake up, Little Red!</font>

12
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:53,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Lynn?</font>

13
00:00:55,440 --> 00:00:57,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What in the world happened to me?</font>

14
00:00:57,910 --> 00:01:01,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were fighting somebody 
and got knocked out, Leah.</font>

15
00:01:01,800 --> 00:01:03,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Protect.</font>

16
00:01:03,150 --> 00:01:04,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Protecting.</font>

17
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:06,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that's right! The painting!</font>

18
00:01:06,690 --> 00:01:07,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

19
00:01:07,920 --> 00:01:09,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's gone?</font>

20
00:01:09,720 --> 00:01:10,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was it a painting of?</font>

21
00:01:11,370 --> 00:01:16,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Alas, I was uncharacteristically taken 
by surprise, so I didn't get a good look.</font>

22
00:01:17,260 --> 00:01:18,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Watch out, Lynn!</font>

23
00:01:22,240 --> 00:01:24,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-Thank you very much!</font>

24
00:01:24,590 --> 00:01:28,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not at all. I was simply returning
 the marvelous favor.</font>

25
00:01:32,330 --> 00:01:34,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They just keep coming, huh?</font>

26
00:01:35,900 --> 00:01:38,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Assemble.</font>

27
00:01:50,880 --> 00:01:53,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take that.</font>

28
00:02:15,250 --> 00:02:19,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There was a gentleman standing
 in front of the painting.</font>

29
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:25,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was almost as if the painting 
thirsted for his blood.</font>

30
00:02:26,550 --> 00:02:32,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The raw, ominous odor of blood filled 
the room in a very, very <i>un</i>-marvelous way.</font>

31
00:02:32,440 --> 00:02:33,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The painting wanted blood?</font>

32
00:02:34,940 --> 00:02:36,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Lynn, what next?</font>

33
00:02:36,890 --> 00:02:39,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We go find Lord Arne, of course.</font>

34
00:02:39,640 --> 00:02:43,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, a marvelous operation 
to rescue Lord Vampire it is.</font>

35
00:02:43,420 --> 00:02:44,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

36
00:02:50,030 --> 00:02:51,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Arne!</font>

37
00:02:55,590 --> 00:02:58,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm impressed you've made it this far.</font>

38
00:02:58,350 --> 00:02:59,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My compliments.</font>

39
00:03:00,030 --> 00:03:01,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course I did.</font>

40
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:03,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Lord Arne's assistant, after all.</font>

41
00:03:04,090 --> 00:03:07,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And now, it is time for you to die.</font>

42
00:03:07,720 --> 00:03:09,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will not allow that.</font>

43
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:13,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You briefly managed to gain the upper hand 
thanks to an underhanded ambush,</font>

44
00:03:13,140 --> 00:03:15,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I, Little Red Phantom Thief,</font>

45
00:03:15,230 --> 00:03:18,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">will marvelously finish you off
 once and for all!</font>

46
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:18,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Lynn, let me handle this.</font>

47
00:03:37,460 --> 00:03:39,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm on my way, Lord Arne.</font>

48
00:04:08,510 --> 00:04:11,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Watch out!</font>

49
00:04:12,340 --> 00:04:13,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Lynn!</font>

50
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:15,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Protect!</font>

51
00:04:24,180 --> 00:04:25,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Zombie guys!</font>

52
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Lynn...</font>

53
00:04:28,450 --> 00:04:30,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Protected.</font>

54
00:04:34,380 --> 00:04:35,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, zombie guys.</font>

55
00:04:38,230 --> 00:04:40,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for your sacrifice.</font>

56
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:47,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Return Lord Arne to me now.</font>

57
00:04:50,740 --> 00:04:53,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like you've run out 
of friends to protect you.</font>

58
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:57,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you still think 
you're going to rescue Neuntöte?</font>

59
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:12,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, you are no more than my plaything.</font>

60
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:28,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't control my body.</i></font>

61
00:05:42,150 --> 00:05:45,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pray tell, why do you go to 
such extreme lengths to save him?</font>

62
00:05:46,370 --> 00:05:51,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because Lord Arne is Neuntöte,
 the ultimate vampire,</font>

63
00:05:51,220 --> 00:05:54,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and a magnificent detective who has 
earned the trust and respect of many.</font>

64
00:05:55,670 --> 00:05:57,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Trust and respect?</font>

65
00:05:58,990 --> 00:06:03,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Additionally, Lord Arne puts 
his faith in me as his assistant.</font>

66
00:06:03,840 --> 00:06:06,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I feel obliged to live up to that faith.</font>

67
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:08,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Preposterous.</font>

68
00:06:08,700 --> 00:06:12,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vampires are sublime beings 
that rule over the entire world.</font>

69
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:17,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To us, humans are mere livestock.
 Nothing but food.</font>

70
00:06:17,630 --> 00:06:21,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is inconceivable that one of us 
would have faith in you as such.</font>

71
00:06:21,440 --> 00:06:23,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are mistaken.</font>

72
00:06:23,670 --> 00:06:28,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">While Lord Arne has not spoken 
of it directly, I understand him.</font>

73
00:06:29,260 --> 00:06:33,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Arne is far too intelligent to 
discriminate between humans and vampires</font>

74
00:06:33,660 --> 00:06:35,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">in such a vulgar way.</font>

75
00:06:35,430 --> 00:06:38,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Arne respects me 
for the person I am.</font>

76
00:06:38,970 --> 00:06:42,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He accepts me as Lynn Reinweiß.</font>

77
00:06:42,620 --> 00:06:47,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that, Mister Vlad, is what 
makes you and him very different.</font>

78
00:06:48,880 --> 00:06:51,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Spare me your delusions.</font>

79
00:06:51,830 --> 00:06:54,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Neuntöte only made you his assistant</font>

80
00:06:54,760 --> 00:06:57,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">because he assumed 
you would be a valuable tool.</font>

81
00:07:03,820 --> 00:07:05,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If that is indeed the case...</font>

82
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:08,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If he did see some value in me,</font>

83
00:07:08,910 --> 00:07:11,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I could not possibly be more honored.</font>

84
00:07:16,710 --> 00:07:18,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, feel honored now...</font>

85
00:07:19,250 --> 00:07:22,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to witness the spectacle
 of Neuntöte's death.</font>

86
00:07:25,460 --> 00:07:26,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know...</font>

87
00:07:27,020 --> 00:07:29,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you enjoy dancing so much,
allow me to cut in.</font>

88
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:32,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For I make a <i>marvelous</i> partner.</font>

89
00:07:34,940 --> 00:07:36,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, Lady Lynn. Hurry.</font>

90
00:07:36,660 --> 00:07:37,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-All right!</font>

91
00:07:50,370 --> 00:07:53,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Arne. I've finally made it.</font>

92
00:08:01,980 --> 00:08:03,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Arne!</font>

93
00:08:05,650 --> 00:08:06,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What the...</font>

94
00:08:06,840 --> 00:08:09,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where the hell am I? <i>Who</i> the hell am I?!</font>

95
00:08:09,600 --> 00:08:12,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm so sorry! I slipped.</font>

96
00:08:16,350 --> 00:08:17,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give it here.</font>

97
00:08:17,260 --> 00:08:18,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

98
00:08:18,350 --> 00:08:19,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This.</font>

99
00:08:40,610 --> 00:08:43,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm back, baby!</font>

100
00:08:49,850 --> 00:08:52,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So we meet again, Vlad.</font>

101
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:57,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that you, Nachzehrer?</font>

102
00:08:57,260 --> 00:08:59,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, so <i>now</i> you remember me?</font>

103
00:08:59,350 --> 00:09:02,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That <i>supremely</i> pisses me off!</font>

104
00:09:23,500 --> 00:09:25,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup, this body seriously rocks.</font>

105
00:09:25,950 --> 00:09:29,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Very nicely timed transformation there,
 Lord Plushie.</font>

106
00:09:29,100 --> 00:09:30,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who are you calling a plushie?!</font>

107
00:09:30,780 --> 00:09:32,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Obviously you, plushie.</font>

108
00:09:34,760 --> 00:09:36,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the hell is so funny?</font>

109
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:44,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm gonna eat you alive!</font>

110
00:09:54,710 --> 00:09:56,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A red moon.</font>

111
00:09:57,430 --> 00:10:00,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just like the moon on that night.</font>

112
00:10:00,950 --> 00:10:06,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When you allowed me to see beyond 
the boundaries of the tiny world I lived in.</font>

113
00:10:06,450 --> 00:10:08,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just like that moon.</font>

114
00:10:12,540 --> 00:10:14,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">L-Lord Arne?</font>

115
00:10:38,650 --> 00:10:39,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There.</font>

116
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:47,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take that!</font>

117
00:10:48,460 --> 00:10:49,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you get him?</font>

118
00:10:56,880 --> 00:10:59,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's simply far too resilient.</font>

119
00:10:59,700 --> 00:11:02,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He ain't got a heart.</font>

120
00:11:02,390 --> 00:11:03,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

121
00:11:04,610 --> 00:11:06,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is becoming tedious.</font>

122
00:11:22,430 --> 00:11:24,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it.</font>

123
00:11:26,770 --> 00:11:30,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm out of blood.</font>

124
00:11:37,130 --> 00:11:38,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you guys okay?</font>

125
00:11:39,280 --> 00:11:40,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leah?</font>

126
00:11:40,330 --> 00:11:42,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nach? Amy?</font>

127
00:11:44,640 --> 00:11:46,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Evilly!</font>

128
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:48,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bloody!</font>

129
00:11:48,510 --> 00:11:50,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fantastic!</font>

130
00:11:50,160 --> 00:11:51,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Neuntöte!</font>

131
00:11:51,830 --> 00:11:54,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's supreme! He can't be beat!</font>

132
00:11:54,120 --> 00:11:56,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We think he's really, really neat!</font>

133
00:11:56,470 --> 00:11:57,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And so vampire-y!</font>

134
00:11:57,920 --> 00:11:59,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you quit fidgeting?</font>

135
00:11:59,610 --> 00:12:02,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Oh, come on! I-I'm obviously acting out
 'cause I'm so embarrassed!</font>

136
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:05,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lynn! Arne!</font>

137
00:12:09,700 --> 00:12:11,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stand aside, Lynn Reinweiß.</font>

138
00:12:11,900 --> 00:12:12,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

139
00:12:13,930 --> 00:12:18,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you that eager to 
get captured again, Neuntöte?</font>

140
00:12:18,330 --> 00:12:19,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean "captured"?</font>

141
00:12:19,950 --> 00:12:22,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was pretty much 
the best nap I've ever had.</font>

142
00:12:35,350 --> 00:12:36,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Arne.</font>

143
00:12:37,250 --> 00:12:38,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Search for it.</font>

144
00:14:17,040 --> 00:14:18,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well played.</font>

145
00:14:19,130 --> 00:14:21,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it seems you've reached your limit.</font>

146
00:14:22,470 --> 00:14:23,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not a chance.</font>

147
00:14:24,410 --> 00:14:26,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And my assistant has found 
something interesting.</font>

148
00:14:40,180 --> 00:14:41,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you found it?</font>

149
00:14:42,380 --> 00:14:43,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

150
00:14:44,080 --> 00:14:46,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A portrait of Vlad himself.</font>

151
00:14:47,160 --> 00:14:49,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm impressed you knew it was here.</font>

152
00:14:49,270 --> 00:14:52,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have the floor plan 
of this entire castle memorized,</font>

153
00:14:52,660 --> 00:14:55,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and while I was looking 
at the place from outside,</font>

154
00:14:55,660 --> 00:14:58,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I noticed a slight inconsistency.</font>

155
00:14:58,980 --> 00:15:01,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I realized there must be
 a hidden chamber,</font>

156
00:15:01,410 --> 00:15:04,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">which wouldn't have been
 included on the map.</font>

157
00:15:04,540 --> 00:15:07,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'd be mistaken if you thought
you can fool the trained eye</font>

158
00:15:07,920 --> 00:15:11,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">of the vampire otaku 
known as Lynn Reinweiß!</font>

159
00:15:18,740 --> 00:15:19,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do it.</font>

160
00:15:19,560 --> 00:15:20,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right!</font>

161
00:15:30,880 --> 00:15:31,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lynn!</font>

162
00:15:36,980 --> 00:15:38,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please stop, Lynn.</font>

163
00:15:47,180 --> 00:15:48,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop right there.</font>

164
00:15:49,160 --> 00:15:50,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please stop.</font>

165
00:15:51,040 --> 00:15:52,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop, honey.</font>

166
00:15:52,520 --> 00:15:53,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's time to stop.</font>

167
00:15:54,330 --> 00:15:55,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop right meow.</font>

168
00:15:56,160 --> 00:15:57,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop.</font>

169
00:15:57,540 --> 00:15:58,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just stop, okay?</font>

170
00:16:00,990 --> 00:16:04,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">May I ask you to stop what 
you are doing, Mistress Lynn?</font>

171
00:16:11,880 --> 00:16:12,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lynn.</font>

172
00:16:20,390 --> 00:16:23,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lynn. My dear, beloved Lynn.</font>

173
00:16:24,480 --> 00:16:26,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come to me.</font>

174
00:16:28,980 --> 00:16:30,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Father.</font>

175
00:16:58,110 --> 00:17:00,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are not my father.</font>

176
00:17:02,240 --> 00:17:02,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lynn?</font>

177
00:17:04,570 --> 00:17:06,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This amulet protects against evil.</font>

178
00:17:06,760 --> 00:17:09,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I already tested it on Nach
so I know it works.</font>

179
00:17:09,750 --> 00:17:12,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It looks like it's effective 
against you as well!</font>

180
00:17:12,880 --> 00:17:15,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What do you intend to do with that?</font>

181
00:17:15,700 --> 00:17:17,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I intend to do...</font>

182
00:17:18,070 --> 00:17:18,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">this!</font>

183
00:17:31,920 --> 00:17:35,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-That was no mere amulet.</font>

184
00:17:35,500 --> 00:17:37,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was full of holy water mixed 
with silver-infused paint.</font>

185
00:17:38,510 --> 00:17:40,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Silver and holy water?</font>

186
00:17:40,910 --> 00:17:44,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vampires are susceptible 
to both silver and holy water.</font>

187
00:17:44,880 --> 00:17:46,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's common knowledge.</font>

188
00:17:50,460 --> 00:17:51,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Arne.</font>

189
00:17:52,300 --> 00:17:53,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He is Vlad the Third.</font>

190
00:17:53,670 --> 00:17:55,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vlad Țepeș.</font>

191
00:17:55,480 --> 00:17:57,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vlad the Impaler.</font>

192
00:17:57,480 --> 00:18:02,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And one of the nine vampire kings.</font>

193
00:18:02,900 --> 00:18:05,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's Count Dracula—and this is his heart!</font>

194
00:18:05,620 --> 00:18:07,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just as we suspected.</font>

195
00:18:09,290 --> 00:18:10,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Evilly.</font>

196
00:18:11,440 --> 00:18:13,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bloody.</font>

197
00:18:13,490 --> 00:18:15,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fantastic.</font>

198
00:18:16,240 --> 00:18:18,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Neuntöte.</font>

199
00:18:19,700 --> 00:18:23,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When did you acquire 
such a horrid weapon?</font>

200
00:18:23,030 --> 00:18:25,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right before I came to this castle.</font>

201
00:18:25,760 --> 00:18:27,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you kindly, kiddo.</font>

202
00:18:30,380 --> 00:18:34,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you <i>really</i> think 
I wouldn't know the weaknesses</font>

203
00:18:34,300 --> 00:18:37,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">of a <i>super</i>-major vampire 
like Count Dracula?</font>

204
00:18:40,720 --> 00:18:41,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now...</font>

205
00:18:42,000 --> 00:18:43,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's see you...</font>

206
00:18:43,930 --> 00:18:47,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">dance joyfully!</font>

207
00:19:10,280 --> 00:19:14,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I warned you not to underestimate
 Lynn Reinweiß.</font>

208
00:19:14,090 --> 00:19:16,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We did it, Lord Arne.</font>

209
00:19:20,280 --> 00:19:21,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Up you go.</font>

210
00:19:22,460 --> 00:19:24,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That really is terrible.</font>

211
00:19:24,250 --> 00:19:25,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How can you say that?</font>

212
00:19:25,830 --> 00:19:28,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is my ultimate masterpiece!</font>

213
00:19:28,480 --> 00:19:30,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Ultimate masterpiece," my fangs.</font>

214
00:19:30,750 --> 00:19:34,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing about this is artistic.
 It's insulting.</font>

215
00:19:34,320 --> 00:19:37,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Neuntöte. This was your idea, wasn't it?</font>

216
00:19:37,680 --> 00:19:41,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'd better not have put the heart
 inside this painting, Zwei.</font>

217
00:19:41,790 --> 00:19:43,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not to worry, Lady Amy.</font>

218
00:19:43,760 --> 00:19:47,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Dracula's heart is safe and sound
 inside Lord Vampire's body.</font>

219
00:19:48,350 --> 00:19:52,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, well, Vlad. Looks like 
you've seen better days, huh?</font>

220
00:19:52,310 --> 00:19:54,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I could say the same about you.</font>

221
00:19:54,130 --> 00:19:55,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The same?</font>

222
00:19:55,560 --> 00:19:58,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But hey, look, I can move and stuff.</font>

223
00:19:59,200 --> 00:20:02,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never imagined a stuffed animal 
would get the better of me.</font>

224
00:20:03,380 --> 00:20:06,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Might as well sharpen my claws a bit.</font>

225
00:20:06,430 --> 00:20:07,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Scratch, scratch.</font>

226
00:20:06,430 --> 00:20:09,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm? Hey. Cut that out, damn it.</font>

227
00:20:07,910 --> 00:20:09,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Scratch, scratch, scratch.</font>

228
00:20:09,350 --> 00:20:14,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Scratch, scratch, scratch, scratch, 
scratch, scratch, scratch, scratch!</font>

229
00:20:09,350 --> 00:20:12,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop clawing at me. 
I said stop with the clawing.</font>

230
00:20:12,770 --> 00:20:14,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you keep it down?</font>

231
00:20:14,920 --> 00:20:15,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey.</font>

232
00:20:18,050 --> 00:20:23,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, Lord Arne, I guess nobody will ever 
be hypnotized by Vlad's paintings again.</font>

233
00:20:23,900 --> 00:20:25,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Most likely.</font>

234
00:20:25,230 --> 00:20:26,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Arne.</font>

235
00:20:26,900 --> 00:20:27,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

236
00:20:27,990 --> 00:20:31,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I went out and fetched 
a new client for you, kiddo.</font>

237
00:20:32,050 --> 00:20:36,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Already jumping into our next case! 
I'd expect nothing less from Lord Arne.</font>

238
00:20:36,920 --> 00:20:39,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? It's already late, man.</font>

239
00:20:41,460 --> 00:20:44,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like it's nighty-night 
for Lord Plushie.</font>

240
00:20:44,060 --> 00:20:46,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you to quit calling me that!</font>

241
00:20:46,720 --> 00:20:50,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Zwei, why not wait and hear 
about the case tomorrow?</font>

242
00:20:51,120 --> 00:20:55,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's right, Arne. There are all sorts of
 rumors in Lugenberg about the agency</font>

243
00:20:55,500 --> 00:20:57,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">being a really toxic workplace.</font>

244
00:20:57,770 --> 00:20:59,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We must not delay!</font>

245
00:20:59,320 --> 00:21:01,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This world is still packed 
full of cases and mysteries</font>

246
00:21:01,940 --> 00:21:05,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that can only be solved 
by the Arne Detective Agency.</font>

247
00:21:06,100 --> 00:21:08,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't that right, Lord Arne?</font>

248
00:21:11,840 --> 00:21:13,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you waiting for?</font>

249
00:21:13,520 --> 00:21:16,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's get going, Lynn Reinweiß.</font>

250
00:21:17,920 --> 00:21:18,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right!</font>

251
00:21:19,920 --> 00:21:22,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}THE CASEBOOK OF ARNE
DRACULA'S FINAL CASE</font>

252
00:21:22,880 --> 00:21:25,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}PART 12: ALL'S WELL THAT ENDS WELL</font>

253
00:21:35,480 --> 00:21:39,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}TRANSLATION: MICHAEL ARNOLD</font>

254
